&lt;h4&gt;01. What is the channel that the wifi-global Access Point is currently using?&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;01-what-is-the-channel-that-the-wifi-global-access-point-is-currently-using&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#01-what-is-the-channel-that-the-wifi-global-access-point-is-currently-using&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Setup the wifi adapter in monitor mode and verify the setup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;$ airmon-ng check &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;kill&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;$ airmon-ng start wlan0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;$ airmon-ng --verbose&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copied!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start &lt;code&gt;airodump-ng&lt;/code&gt; and look for the results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;airodump-ng wlan0mon -w ~/wifi/scan --manufacturer --wps --band abg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copied!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We can also see the output capture files are saved for the further analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;02. What is the MAC of the wifi-IT client?&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;02-what-is-the-mac-of-the-wifi-it-client&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#02-what-is-the-mac-of-the-wifi-it-client&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;From the previous output we can see that the BSSID of the client wifi-IT is &lt;code&gt;F0:9F:C2:1A:CA:25&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using this information we can identify the MAC of the essid &lt;code&gt;wifi-IT&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;airodump-ng wlan0mon --essid wifi-IT --bssid F0:9F:C2:1A:CA:25 -c &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt; --manufacturer --wps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copied!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;03. What is the probe of 78:C1:A7:BF:72:46 ?&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;03-what-is-the-probe-of-78c1a7bf7246-&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#03-what-is-the-probe-of-78c1a7bf7246-&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We can run &lt;code&gt;airodump-ng&lt;/code&gt; again to check the probe of provided address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;airodump-ng wlan0mon -w ~/wifi/scan --manufacturer --wps --band abg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copied!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;04. What is the ESSID of the hidden AP (mac F0:9F:C2:6A:88:26)?&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;04-what-is-the-essid-of-the-hidden-ap-mac-f09fc26a8826&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#04-what-is-the-essid-of-the-hidden-ap-mac-f09fc26a8826&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare a wordlist with the common patterns &lt;code&gt;wifi-$words&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;cat /root/rockyou-top100000.txt | awk &amp;#39;{print &amp;#34;wifi-&amp;#34;$1}&amp;#39; &amp;gt; wifi.wordlist&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copied!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This wordlist will be use to brute force the wifi essids&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Verify the generated list, which looks like the below listed example.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;$ less wifi.wordlist
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;wifi-123456
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;wifi-12345
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;wifi-123456789
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;wifi-12345678
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;wifi-abc123
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;wifi-nicole&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copied!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We can now use &lt;code&gt;mdk4&lt;/code&gt; to bruteforce the essid of the provided address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First find the channel of the provided AP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;$ airodump-ng wlan0mon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copied!&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We can see that it&amp;rsquo;s running in &lt;code&gt;channel 11&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The below explains the options set for the program (refer to mdk4 man page)
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;p&lt;/code&gt; - SSID Probing and Bruteforcing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;-t&lt;/code&gt; - Set MAC address of target AP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;-f&lt;/code&gt; - Read SSIDs from file for bruteforcing hidden SSIDs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code&#34;&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;iwconfig wlan0mon channel &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;mdk4 wlan0mon p -t  F0:9F:C2:6A:88:26 -f ./wifi.wordlist&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    aria-label=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    data-copied-label=&#34;Copied!&#34;
